article.description: Nic Wise hit a 3-pointer at the buzzer in overtime to llift Arizona over Lipscomb on Monday.
article.headline: Wise's 3 at OT horn lifts Arizona over Lipscomb
article.linkText: Wise's 3 at OT horn lifts Arizona over Lipscomb
article.story: TUCSON, Ariz. -- Nic Wise hit a 3-pointer with 0.1 second left in overtime Monday to give Arizona an 83-82 victory over Lipscomb. After Lipscomb's Adnan Hodzic missed the second of two free throws to make it 82-80 with 4.7 seconds left, Arizona got the rebound and scrambled downcourt for a final shot. Wise threw up his desperation shot just as the buzzer sounded. It hit nothing but net. Wise finished with 26 points for the Wildcats (5-5), who are 2-1 in overtime games this season. Hodzic had 34 points for Lipscomb (4-7). The Bison led most of the game before UA's Derrick Williams scored off an offensive rebound to tie it at 52. Lipscomb's Brian Wright hit a 3-pointer with 1.5 seconds left after Jordan Burgason missed a 3-pointer with 3 seconds left to tie it at 69 and send it into overtime.
